snippet.title: RPG Asdivine Dios - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Become a deity and save the world in Asdivine Dios!
RPG Asdivine Dios is available for Android.

Get the Freemium edition now on Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.asdivinediosfree

Get the Premium edition now on Google Play
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=kemco.execreate.asdivinedios

After suddenly losing his magic to a powerful force known as “Murk”, Izayoi, the deity of Asdivine himself sets off on a globe-spanning journey along with a trio of spirits in an effort to save the very world he created. Yet, despite his disdain for humans and their society, will his companions be able to convince him how similar they and the divine really are?

©2015 KEMCO/EXE-CREATE
※All graphics terms, characters and elements are subject to change in the actual product.
